Pool Results across Imputations

gfs_pool_estimates.Rd

TO-DO

Usage

gfs_pool_estimates(data)

Arguments

data

a long.data.frame with at least a .imp column and a fit.tidy

Value

a one-row data.frame with columns * nimp * estimate.pooled * se.pooled * df.approx * t.statistic * f.statistic * ci.low * ci.up * p.value see below for additional information about these statistics

Details

Pool results across imputed datasets using Rubin's Rules.
